{"id": 3130, "genre": 1001, "title": "身为当代年轻人，你都有哪些把烦恼降级的偷懒人生方案？", "description": "如果“过成人生赢家”是plan a的话，我还是备好plan b比较好。（题图来自：iStock ©️Aleksei Morozov）", "record_count": 1806, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20200119155643JWVhUR7F8OvDMBgx.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2020-01-19T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 352002, "content": "逃避困难", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 296361}, {"id": 352003, "content": "说：就这样吧～烦的没有任何意义", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 959289}, {"id": 352259, "content": "卸载微博 屏蔽某些朋友的pyq\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1679613}, {"id": 352515, "content": "睡觉哎～～～", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1687768}, {"id": 352516, "content": "做白日梦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1687817}, {"id": 352517, "content": "把手机关了看书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1264713}, {"id": 352006, "content": "睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677742}, {"id": 352267, "content": "不与三观不合的人辩论某一件事情的对错", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1679825}, {"id": 352274, "content": "混吃等死", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1679858}, {"id": 352275, "content": "吃火锅", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1679858}, {"id": 352531, "content": "不要求完美，别老是想着逼自己，做一个差不多小姐/先生，差不多就行了  哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1688508}, {"id": 352279, "content": "手机一甩\n纵横四海", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674508}, {"id": 352025, "content": "就..只是坐着", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677790}, {"id": 352544, "content": "听听歌，看看小说。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1689110}, {"id": 352041, "content": "就不管他，忙其他能让自己开心的事情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1323768}, {"id": 352554, "content": "跑步", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1690143}, {"id": 352561, "content": "暴饮暴食后在运动😭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1690512}, {"id": 352051, "content": "多运动", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151437}, {"id": 352566, "content": "哎，没有方向，没人指点，没有背景，不然我也一定能成。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1630544}, {"id": 352570, "content": "无所谓ㅍ_ㅍㅍ_ㅍ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1690843}, {"id": 352571, "content": "手机静音", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315624}, {"id": 352316, "content": "首先，是个好问题。可以看看别人的做法。把烦恼降低么:何以解忧——唯有吃、随风奔跑、去外面[宽广的地方]散心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680555}, {"id": 352061, "content": "任何事的发生都是自我修炼", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677862}, {"id": 352575, "content": "游戏啊，番剧啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1690991}, {"id": 352580, "content": "装傻", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1691211}, {"id": 352584, "content": "不要想，去做吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1690540}, {"id": 352587, "content": "人间不值得", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1691564}, {"id": 352337, "content": "拖延，跑神", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221564}, {"id": 352340, "content": "看书", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677395}, {"id": 352596, "content": "自嗨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246920}, {"id": 352600, "content": "你不配让我烦恼 / 我不配拥有烦恼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1692192}, {"id": 352090, "content": "吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664543}, {"id": 352609, "content": "少聊八卦，专注自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938303}, {"id": 352105, "content": "读个博 : )", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677945}, {"id": 352361, "content": "突然换个濒死人格（其实它还带着可以压榨我的纵容的技能)，它狠狠对我说话，并夺走且掌握身体控制权，之后它会帮我做出拒绝的决定，总像帮我处理死前后事一样，【当然首先我得先表示出妥协且放手不管的逃避姿态】……(>_<)", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1681643}, {"id": 352619, "content": "拒绝成功学，拒绝鸡血式鸡汤文", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034498}, {"id": 352365, "content": "少看手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1627030}, {"id": 352626, "content": "闭目养神", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1693062}, {"id": 352372, "content": "听喜欢的音乐，多看书籍。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1463799}, {"id": 352373, "content": "尽量躺在床上不动，连饭都可以省了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506438}, {"id": 352377, "content": "不要拧巴任何已经知道了结果的事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1682170}, {"id": 352389, "content": "勤入厨房勤上床，\n多搞运动多阅读，\n少玩游戏少熬夜", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1682689}, {"id": 352645, "content": "降低期望值，对能让自己开心的事感兴趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1693615}, {"id": 352650, "content": "👀看  记录别人的美好生活……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1693708}, {"id": 352395, "content": "少管闲事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1682784}, {"id": 352150, "content": "天灾人祸不知道明天跟意外哪个先来临所以做一天人就快活一天吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1099645}, {"id": 352406, "content": "斩断念想，果断放手，得不到的就是得不到的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1582450}, {"id": 352408, "content": "转移注意力", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1683738}, {"id": 352153, "content": "吃饭睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1678172}, {"id": 352665, "content": "投入自己认真做事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1685643}]}